MAGIC ITEMS
===========
- Ring of Life: immune to defiling penalties
- Amulet of Psionic Interference (cursed): wearer can't make any power checks
- Rod of Water Divining: Y-shaped rod that points towards the nearest water source within 1 km.
- BOTANICAL ENCHANTMENT: create potion fruit trees

	REMOVED
	OK - bottle of endless water
	OK - horseshoes (all)
	OK - stone horse
	OK - elven chain
	OK - any aquatic-related item
	OK - any lycanthrope-related item

	CHANGED
	- candle of invocation: only spirits of the lands and elementals
	OK - figurines of wondrous power: only ebony fly and golden lion
	- prayer beads: summons powerful elemental, instead


